---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Terms of Service — KAIRA"
  description="Terms of service for KAIRA's website and web design, SEO, and maintenance services."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 py-16 md:py-20">
    <p class="hud-label mb-3">LEGAL · TERMS</p>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink md:text-4xl">Terms of <span class="grad-text">Service</span></h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-muted">Last updated: July 17, 2026</p>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-8 text-ink-soft leading-relaxed [&_h2]:text-xl [&_h2]:font-bold [&_h2]:text-ink">
      <section>
        <h2>1. About these terms</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          These terms govern your use of the KAIRA website and describe how our services are
          engaged. Submitting a quote request does not create a contract; specific project terms are
          agreed in a written proposal or agreement before work begins.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>2. Services & quotes</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          Pricing shown on this site (including “websites starting at $1,000”) is indicative.
          Every project is quoted individually based on scope. A quote becomes binding only when
          accepted in writing by both parties.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>3. Payment</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          Unless otherwise agreed, projects require a deposit before work begins, with the balance
          due at launch. Invoices are issued through Stripe. Recurring services (maintenance, SEO)
          are billed monthly and may be canceled with written notice as described in your agreement.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>4. Intellectual property</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          Upon full payment, you own the final website deliverables created for your project. KAIRA
          retains the right to display completed work in its portfolio unless agreed otherwise.
          Portfolio items labeled “Concept Project” are fictional demonstrations and do not
          represent real client engagements.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>5. Warranties & liability</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          We build to modern professional standards, but no website can be guaranteed to be
          error-free or to achieve specific search rankings or business results. To the fullest
          extent permitted by law, KAIRA's total liability for any claim is limited to the amount
          you paid for the services giving rise to the claim.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>6. Changes</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          We may update these terms from time to time. The “last updated” date above reflects the
          current version. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>7. Contact</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          Questions? Reach us through the <a href="/contact" class="font-medium text-purple hover:underline">contact form</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
